724
00:44:38,565 --> 00:44:41,365
Astaga.
Kapan kau terpapar ?

725
00:44:41,367 --> 00:44:43,168
Sekitar 30 jam lalu.

726
00:44:43,170 --> 00:44:44,635
Berarti kapsul berisi virus...

727
00:44:44,637 --> 00:44:47,072
